    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: Report Info: Project value propositions (Speed, Community, Fair Launch). -> Goal: Inform and build trust. -> Viz/Presentation Method: Thematic icon-driven feature cards using structured HTML/CSS and Unicode characters. -> Interaction: Subtle hover-and-scale effects on cards to provide interactive feedback. -> Justification: For a meme coin without historical data, traditional charts are irrelevant. Icon-based cards are more effective for communicating core concepts quickly and visually, reinforcing the brand identity. The goal is persuasion and branding, not data analysis. -> Library/Method: Tailwind CSS for layout and styling; Unicode/Emoji for icons. -->
